nodes.text: Tebien Ros was a Human male who lived on Nar Shaddaa during the Cold War. He had a shop on the Promenade, where he built and sold blasters and other weaponry.

Tebien Ros was created for Star Wars: The Old Republic, a massively multiplayer online role-playing game released by BioWare on December 20, 2011. He appears on Nar Shaddaa as an Armstech crew skill trainer.
